Fuzzy transfromcijas un to lietojumi Volterra integrlviendojumu risinan.

aj rakst tiek aplkota fuzzy transfromcija un k t tiek leitota skaitliskai integrlviendojumu risinan.

Defincija

Lai $x_{1} < \ldots < x_{n}$ ir fiksti punkti intervl [a,b] t, ka $a=x_{1}, x_{n} = b$ un $n \geq 2$. Tad nestrikts kopas $A_{1}, \ldots, A_{n}$ ar attiecgi piederbas funkcijm $A_{1}(x), \ldots, A_{n}(x)$, kuras ir defintas intervl [a,b], ir bzes funkcijas, ja izpilds:

  1. $A_{k}(x):[a,b]\to[0,1]$
  2. $A_{k}(x)=0 $, ja $x\notin (x_{k-1},x_{k+1})$
  3. $A_{k}$ ir neprtraukta
  4. $A_{k}(x)$, $k=2,\ldots,n$ stingri aug, kad $x\in [x_{k-1},x_{k}]$ un $ A_{k}(x)$, $k= 1, \ldots n-1 $ stringri dilst, kad $ x\in [x_{k},x_{k+1}] $
  5. $\forall x\in [a,b], \sum\limits^{n}_{k=1} A_{k}(x)= 1 $

Piemrs

Trijstra bzes funckijas

$$ A_{1}(x) = \begin{cases} 1 - \frac{x- x_{1}}{h_{1}} \text{ if } x \in [x_{1},x_{2}]\\ 0 \text{ citdi } \end{cases} $$$$ A_{k}(x) = \begin{cases} \frac{x- x_{k-1}}{h_{k-1}} \text{ if } x \in [x_{k-1},x_{k}]\\ 1 - \frac{x- x_{k}}{h_{k}} \text{ if } x \in [x_{k},x_{k+1}]\\ 0 \text{ citdi } \end{cases} $$$$ A_{n}(x) = \begin{cases} \frac{x- x_{n-1}}{h_{n-1}} \text{ if } x \in [x_{n-1},x_{n}]\\ 0 \text{ citdi } \end{cases} $$

Turpmk visiem $k = 1,\ldots, n$ tiks lietots vienmrgs soa garums, $ h = \frac{b-a}{n-1}$

In[]:
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from PIL import Image

import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore")

def bazes_fun(k,a,b):

    # soa garums
    h = (b-a)/(k-1)

    # reis
    xx_k = np.arange(a,b+h,h)

    # Saraksts bzes funkcijm
    A_basic_fun = []

    ### Tlk devin trijstra bzes funkcijas

    # Vispirms pirmo (lab trijstra mala)
    A_basic_fun.append(lambda x: max(0, 1 -(x[0]-xx_k[0])/h))

    for id_x, xk in enumerate(xx_k[1:-1],start =1):
        A_basic_fun.append( lambda x:  max( min(  (x[0]- xx_k[x[1]-1])/h, 1- ( x[0] - xx_k[x[1]])/h ),0 ))

    # Beigs pievieno pdjo (tikai kreis mala trijstrim)
    A_basic_fun.append( lambda x:  max(0,  ( x[0]-xx_k[-2])/h))

    return [A_basic_fun,h,xx_k]

Fuzzy-transform jeb F-transform

Definija (integrl transformcija)

Lai $A_{1}, \ldots, A_{n}$ ir bzes funkcijas intervla [a,b] un f ir kda neprtrautka funckija $f\in C([a,b])$, tad vektors $ \textbf{F}_{n}[f] = [F_{1}, \ldots F_{n}]$ ir funkcijas F-transformcija, kur

$$ F_{k} = \frac{\int^{b}_{a}A_{k}(x)f(x)dx}{\int^{b}_{a}A_{k}(x)dx} $$

Ir spk

$$ F_{1} = \frac{2}{h} \int_{x_{1}}^{x_{2}} f(x)A_{1}(x) dx$$$$ F_{n} = \frac{2}{h} \int_{x_{n-1}}^{x_{n}} f(x)A_{n}(x) dx$$$$ F_{k} = \frac{1}{h} \int_{x_{k-1}}^{x_{k+1}} f(x)A_{k}(x) dx, k = 2,\ldots n-1$$
In[]:
import scipy.integrate as integrate

def F_transform(f,A,h,xx_k):
    F_t = []
    F_t.append(2/h* integrate.quad(lambda x: f(x) *A[0]([x,0]) , xx_k[0], xx_k[1])[0])
    for id_x, x_k in enumerate(xx_k[1:-1],start =1):
        F_t.append( 1/h * integrate.quad(lambda x: f(x) * A[id_x]([x,id_x]) , xx_k[id_x-1], xx_k[id_x+1])[0] )
    F_t.append(  2/h * integrate.quad(lambda x: f(x) * A[-1]([x,-1]) , xx_k[-2], xx_k[-1])[0]  )
    return F_t

Defincija

Lai $A_{1}, \ldots A_{n}$ ir bzes funkcijas intervl [a,b], $f\in C([a,b])$ un $ \textbf{F}_{n}[f] = [F_{1},\ldots F_{n}]$ ir funkciajs f integrl F-transformcija attiecb pret bzes funkcijm $A_{1}, \ldots A_{n}$. Tad invers transformcija

$$ f_{F,n}(x) = \sum^{n}_{k=1}F_{k}A_{k}(x)$$

Teorma

Lai f ir neprtraukta intervl [a,b]. Tad katram $\varepsilon > 0 $ eksist tds $n_{\varepsilon} $ un bzes funkcijas $A_{1}, \ldots A_{n_{\varepsilon}}$ t, ka ja $x\in [a,b]$, tad $ \big| f(x) - f_{F,n_{\varepsilon}}(x) \big| \leq \varepsilon $

kur $f_{F,n_{\varepsilon}}$ ir funkcijas f invers F-transformcija pret $A_{1}, \ldots, A_{n_{\varepsilon}}$

In[]:
# Dotaj punkt atrod inverso f transformciju.
def inversa_transformacija(x,F_k,A):
    inversa_vert = 0

    for id, funkcija in enumerate(A):
        inversa_vert +=  funkcija([x,id]) * F_k[id]

    return inversa_vert

Ldzgi k tas bija iepriekj piemr, pie lielkm n vrtbm, invers transfromcija sasniedz funkciju f.

Diskrt F-tranfromcija

Defincija

Lai funkcijas f vrtbas ir uzdotas punktos $p_{1}, \ldots p_{l} \in [a,b]$ un $A_{1}, \ldots A_{n}$ n < l ir bzes funkijas kop [a,b]. Tad vektors $[F_{1}, \ldots, F_{n}]$ ir funkcijas f diksrt F-transformcija attiecb pret $A_{1}, \ldots, A_{n}$, ja $$ F_{k} = \frac{\sum^{l}_{j=1} f(p_{j})A_{k}(p_{j})}{ \sum^{l}_{j=1} A_{k}(p_{j}) } $$

Defincija

Lai funkcijas f vrtbas ir uzdotas punktos $p_{1}, \ldots p_{l} \in [a,b]$ un $ \vec{F_{n}}[f] = [F_{1}, \ldots F_{n}]$ ir funkcijas f diskrt F-transformcija attiecb pret $A_{1}, \ldots, A_{n}$. Tad

$$ f_{F,n}(p_{j}) = \sum^{n}_{k=1} F_{k} A_{k}(p_{j})$$

Divarguemntu funkciju F-transformcija

Defincija

Lai $A_{1}, \ldots A_{n}$ ir bzes funkcijas intervl [a,b] un lai $B_{1}, \ldots, B_{m}$ ir bzes funkcijas intervl [c,d]. Lai $f(x,y) \in C([a,b] \times [c,d])$. Tad $n \times m $ matrica $ \textbf{F}_{n,m}[f]= (F_{kl})$ ir integrl F-transfromcija funkcijai f attiecb pret funkcijm A un B ar

$$ F_{kl} = \frac{ \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{k}(x) B_{l}(y) dx dy }{ \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} A_{k}(x) B_{l}(y) dxdy} $$

Defincija

Lai funkcija f ir uzdota punktos $ (p_{i}, q_{j}) \in [a,b] \times [c,d] , i= 1,\ldots ,N , j = 1, \ldots, M$ un $A_{1}, \ldots, A_{n}, B_{1}, \ldots B_{m}$ ar n< N un m< M, ir bzes funckijas. Tad $n \times m $ matrica $ \textbf{F}_{n,m}[f]= (F_{kl})$ ir disrkt F-transfromcija funkcijai f attiecb pret funkcijm A un B ar

$$ F_{kl} = \frac{ \sum^{M}_{j=1} \sum^{N}_{i=1} f(p_{i},q_{j})A_{k}(p_{i})B_{l}(q_{j})}{ \sum^{M}_{j=1} \sum^{N}_{i=1} A_{k}(p_{i})B_{l}(q_{j})}$$

Divu dimensiju gadjum, integrlo F-transfromciju var vienkrot

$$ F_{11} = \frac{ 4}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{1}(x) B_{1}(y) dx dy $$$$ F_{1m} = \frac{ 4}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{1}(x) B_{m}(y) dx dy $$$$ F_{n1} = \frac{ 4}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{n}(x) B_{1}(y) dx dy $$$$ F_{nm} = \frac{ 4}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{n}(x) B_{m}(y) dx dy $$

un pie $ k= 2, \ldots n-1 $ un $ l = 2 \ldots m-1$

$$ F_{k1} = \frac{ 2}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{k}(x) B_{1}(y) dx dy $$$$ F_{km} = \frac{ 2}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{k}(x) B_{m}(y) dx dy $$$$ F_{1l} = \frac{ 2}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{1}(x) B_{l}(y) dx dy $$$$ F_{nl} = \frac{ 2}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{n}(x) B_{l}(y) dx dy $$$$ F_{kl} = \frac{ 1}{ h_{1} h_{2}} \int^{d}_{c} \int^{b}_{a} f(x,y) A_{k}(x) B_{l}(y) dx dy $$

eit $h_{1} = \frac{b-c}{n-1}$ un $ h_{2} = \frac{d-c}{m-1}$

2D diskrts F-transformcijas lietojuma attlu saspiean

Vispirms dotajam attlam tiek pieleitota 2d diskrt F-transformcija. Pc tam im attlam tiek atrasta invers F-transformcija.

Kv = [5,21,41]

img = Image.open("attels.jpg")
img_gray = img.convert('L')
img_array = np.array(img_gray)
attels_x = img_array.shape[0]
attels_y = img_array.shape[1]

for k in Kv:
    [A_x,hx, xx_xk] =bazes_fun(k,0,attels_x)
    [B_y, hy, xx_yk] =bazes_fun(k,0,attels_y)
    attels_transfromacija = np.zeros((k,k))

    # atrod diskrto F-transfromciju
    for it, Ai in enumerate(A_x):
        for jt, Bj in enumerate(B_y):
            skaititajs = 0
            saucejs = 0
            for i in range(attels_x):
                for j in range(attels_y):
                
                    skaititajs += img_array[i][j] * Ai([i,it])*Bj([j,jt])
                    saucejs += Ai([i,it])*Bj([j,jt])

            attels_transfromacija[it][jt] = skaititajs/saucejs

    fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2)
    inversa_transformacija =np.zeros((attels_x,attels_y))
    # Atrod inverso F-transfromciju.
    for i in range(attels_x):
        for j in range(attels_y):
            for it, Ai in enumerate(A_x):
                for jt, Bj in enumerate(B_y):
                    inversa_transformacija[i][j] += attels_transfromacija[it][jt] *Ai([i,it])*Bj([j,jt])

    axes[0, 0].imshow(img_array, cmap='gray')  
    axes[0, 0].axis('off')  
    axes[0, 0].set_title(" Oriinlais attls")  
    axes[0, 1].imshow(attels_transfromacija, cmap='gray') 
    axes[0, 1].axis('off')  
    axes[0, 1].set_title("2d F-transfromcija")  
    axes[1, 0].imshow(inversa_transformacija, cmap='gray')  
    axes[1, 0].axis('off')  
    axes[1, 0].set_title(" Invers transformcija")  
    axes[1, 1].axis('off')  
    fig.suptitle("k = " + str(k))
    plt.subplots_adjust(top=0.8)

    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

F-transformcijas lietojums Volterra integrlviendojumu risinan

Volterra integrlviendojums

$$ u(t) = g(t) + \lambda \int^{t}_{a}k(t,s) u(s) ds $$

kur $t\in [a,b]$, $ \lambda \in \mathbb{R} \setminus \{ 0\} $, $k:[a,b]\times \mathbb{R} \to [a,b]$, $g:[a,b] \to \mathbb{R}$ un nezinm funkcija $u:[a,b] \to \mathbb{R}$

Ir zinms, ja funkcija k ir integrjama un ierobeota un $ g \in L^{2}[a,b]$.

Defincija

Lai $f \in C[a,b] $ . Par linero Volterra (integrlo) operatoru $\mathcal{V} :C[a,b] \to C[a,b]$ sauc

$$ \mathcal{V}(f)(t) = \int^{t}_{a} f(s) ds $$

kur $t\in [a,b] $

Lemma

Lai $ A = [A_{1}, \ldots , A_{n}] $ ir bzes funkcijas intervl [a,b]. Tad katram $i \in \{1, \ldots, n \}$ pielietojot Volterra operatoru $\mathcal{V}$ i-tajai bzes funkcijai

$$ \mathcal{V}(A_{i})(t) = \int^{t}_{a} A_{i}(\tau) d \tau \approx \sum^{n}_{j=1} p_{i,j} A_{j}(t) $$

kur $ p_{i,j} = \int^{x_{j}}_{a} A_{i}(\tau) d \tau $, $i,j = 1,2, \ldots, n $

Defincija

Lai $A = [A_{1}, \ldots A_{n}] $ ir bzes funkcijjas intervl [a,b]. Volterra operatora matrica kop C[a,b] attiecb pret A ir $n\times n $ matrica $P = (p_{i,j})$, kas doti pc iepriekjs formulas.

Sekas

Matrica

$$P = \frac{h}{2} \begin{bmatrix} 0 & 1 & 1 & 1 & \ldots & 1 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 1 & 2 & 2 & \ldots & 2 & 2 & 2 \\ 0 & 0 & 1 & 2 & \ldots & 2 & 2 & 2 \\ \vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots & \vdots & \vdots \\ 0 & 0 & 0 & 0 & \ldots & 0 & 0 & 1 \\ \end{bmatrix} $$

Teorma

Lai $A(t) = [A_{1}(t), \ldots, A_{n}(t)]^T$ ir bzes funkciju vektors un $f\in C[a,b]$. Tad

$$ \mathcal{V}[f](t) \approx F^{T}[f]P A(t) $$

kur F[f] ir funkcijas f F-transformcija attiecb pret bzes funkcijm $A_{1}, \ldots , A_{n}$

In[]:
def matrica_p(k,h):
    P = np.zeros((k,k))
    P[0] +=1
    P[0][0] = 0
    for id in range(1,k):
        P[id][id] = 1
        if id < k-1:
            P[id][id+1:k] =2
    P = P * h/2
    return P

Tlk tiek piedvts piemrs, kur tiek ilustrta iepriek mint teorija. Tiek lietots iepriek mintais polinoms intervl [0,3]. Katr punkt atrasta $\mathcal{V}$ un F transformcija.

F_t = F_transform(f,A,h,xx_k)
P = matrica_p(k,h)

X = np.arange(a,b+0.01,0.01)
Y_VoltTrans = []
Y_FTrans = []

for xi in X:
    # Volterra transformcijas vtba dotaj punkt
    Y_VoltTrans.append(integrate.quad(lambda x: f(x) , a, xi)[0])

    # Katr punkt atrod vrtbas vektoram A(t)
    A_vektors = np.zeros((k,1))
    for id, fun in enumerate(A):
        A_vektors[id][0] = fun([xi,id])
    # F-transormcijas vr'tiba dotaj punkt
    Y_FTrans.append(np.dot( np.dot(F_t,P),A_vektors)[0])

plt.plot(X,Y_VoltTrans)
plt.plot(X, Y_FTrans)
plt.show()

Defincija

Lai $f\in C[a,b]$. un lai $k(t,s)\in [a,b]\times [a,b]$ btu neprtrauktai kodola funkcija apakkop $a \leq s \leq t \leq b$. Par (linero) Volterra-kernel operatoru $ \mathcal{V}_{k}: C[a,b] \to C[a,b]$ ir defints

$$ \mathcal{V}_{k}(f)(t) = \int^{t}_{a} k(t,s) f(s) ds $$

kur $t\in [a,b]$

Tagad skotnjo viendojumu var prrakstt

$$ u(t) = g(t) + \lambda \mathcal{V}_{k}(u)(t) $$

Teorma

Lai $A = [A_{1}, \ldots , A_{n}] $ ir bzes funkcijas intervl [a,b], $u\in C([a,b])$, $k \in C^{2}([a,b] \times [a,b]) $

un $A(t) = (A_{1}(t),\ldots, A_{n}(t))$, tad

$$ \mathcal{V}_{k}(u)(t) \approx U^{T}(K^{T} \odot P)A(t) $$

kur $ U = (U_{1},\ldots , U_{n}) $ ir funkcijas u F-transfromcija, K ir funkcijas k F-transformcijas matrica attiecb pret funkcijm $A = (A_{1}, \ldots, A_{n}) $

Skaitlisk metode integrlviendojuma risinanai

Vlreiz aplko viendojumu

$$ u(t) = g(t) + \lambda \mathcal{V}_{k}(u)(t) $$

aizvieto funkcijas ar to inversm F-transformcijm un iegst

$$ U^{T} A(t) = G^{T}A(t) + \lambda U^{T}(K^{T} \odot P) A(t) $$

Izsldz funkciju A(t)

$$ U^{T} = G^{T} + \lambda U^{T}(K^{T} \odot P) $$

un no dot viendojuma izsaka matricu U

$$ U = (I - \lambda (K^{T} \odot P^{T}) )^{-1} G$$

kas auj atrast funkcijas u F-transformciju. Tlk atliek atrast inverso transformciju, reizinot $ \hat{ u}_{n} = U A(t)$

Piemri

$$ u(t) = 1 - \int^{t}_{a} (t-s) u(s) ds $$

kur $t\in [0,1]$. Viendojuma atrisinjums ir $ u(t) = cos(t)$

In[]:
def _2d_transfromacija(f,A,k,h):
    F_t_2d = np.zeros((k,k))

    for i in range(0,k):
        for j in range(0,k):
            F_t_2d[i][j] = integrate.dblquad(lambda y,x: f([y,x])* A[i]([y,i]) *A[j]([x,j]), a, b, a, b)[0]


    F_t_2d[:,0] *= 2 
    F_t_2d[:,-1] *= 2 
    F_t_2d[0, :] *= 2 
    F_t_2d[-1, :] *= 2 
    F_t_2d *= 1/(h**2)


    return F_t_2d

#funkcija g = 1 
g_t = lambda x: 1

# Kodola funkcija k(t,s)
kodola_fun = lambda x:  (x[0] - x[1])

lmbda = -1

k=15
a=0
b=1

[A,h,xx_k] = bazes_fun(k,a,b)
F_t = F_transform(g_t,A,h,xx_k)
P = matrica_p(k,h)

# Atrod kodola funkcijas trasnfromciju 
# ! is solis ir lns 
K_t = _2d_transfromacija(kodola_fun,A,k,h)


# Funkcijas U F-transformcija
U = np.transpose(  np.dot( np.linalg.inv(  np.identity(k) - lmbda *np.transpose (  np.transpose(K_t) * P) ) , F_t) )

X = np.arange(a,b+0.01,0.01)
Y_Trans = []

plt.plot(X, np.cos(X))

for xi in X:
    A_vektors = np.zeros((k,1))
    for id, fun in enumerate(A):
        A_vektors[id] = fun([xi,id])
    Y_Trans.append(np.dot(U,A_vektors)[0])

plt.plot(X,Y_Trans)
plt.show()
